[{"id":"VH962447","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents two blocks arranged side by side on a horizontal surface. The block on the left is labeled A, and the block on the right is labeled B. The blocks are being pulled to the right by a string. The string extends from the right side of the block A, to the left side of block B. A rightward pointing arrow, labeled F, extends from the right side of block B.\" height=\"114\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH962447.g07.png\" width=\"400\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Blocks <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A,\"><math alttext=\"A,\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>A</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>B</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> of equal mass are on a horizontal surface and are connected by a light string. The blocks are pulled to the right by a horizontal force of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F\"><math alttext=\"F\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>F</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> exerted on block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>B</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. There is negligible friction between the blocks and the horizontal surface. The blocks are accelerating to the right along the surface. Which of the following figures accurately represents the magnitudes and directions of the horizontal forces on the blocks?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH962447_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a diagram of block A, and block B. The blocks are side by side, with block A, on th